    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
