    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that provides a razor-sharp throttle response across the entire power band. This specimen is mechanically impeccable: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS hub and seals have been upgraded to exceed factory specifications. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains a showroom-quality finish with zero paint correction required, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and free of typical bolster wear. Riding on staggered forged alloys with a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key investment for the serious M-division aficionado.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
