    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple and free of any creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity audio system to the adaptive driver aids, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with every scheduled maintenance performed at the dealership. With zero paint chips, no curb rash on the wheels, and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key opportunity for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
